'''Ivy''' is a resident of a building that had a large fire.

==History==
Ivy was in her apartment when a fire broke out in her neighbor, [[Naomi|Naomi's]], apartment. When she realized where the fire was, Ivy tried to refuse to evacuate, but Theo was able to get her out of the building to safety.

==Relationships==
===Familial===
She, [[Caleb (A House Is Not a Home)|Caleb]], and [[Naomi]] are friends. When Naomi wasn't answering her door after calling for help with a burn, Ivy tried to refuse to evacuate without her.
